## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Animation state properly initialized in UIModel
- [ ] Animation tick loop starts on Init and runs continuously
- [ ] Focused column border color pulses smoothly (2.5 second cycle)
- [ ] Pulse is subtle, not distracting
- [ ] No performance degradation (maintains ~60fps)
- [ ] All existing functionality remains unchanged
- [ ] Tests pass

## Notes

- The pulse should be subtle: users shouldn't notice it consciously, but should feel the UI is "alive"
- Color interpolation can be improved later with proper RGB blending (simple version is fine for now)
- Animation loop runs at ~60fps but can throttle if performance is an issue
- This is the foundation for all other arcade effects

