## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Pressing Enter triggers bright border flash (48ms duration)
- [ ] Flash intensity decays smoothly to normal
- [ ] Multiple rapid Enter presses each trigger separate flash
- [ ] Flash does not interfere with pulse animation
- [ ] Focus transitions feel responsive
- [ ] Flash effect is satisfying without being distracting
- [ ] All existing functionality works correctly
- [ ] Tests pass

## Notes

- The 48ms flash duration is brief but noticeable (3 frames at 60fps)
- Flash color should be very bright for impact
- If focus transition is too complex, can skip it - lock-in flash is the priority
- Consider adding lock-in flash to other selection points (sidebar, confirm view)
- Flash effect is what gives the arcade "button press" feel

## Dependencies

- Depends on: bb-cj8-anim-foundation (animation system must exist first)

## Blocks

